e=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d72ae89b-162c-4f08-918c-ab9a7abfcbab\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>전개도 및 모형</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9c78a854-ffe3-497b-996e-5d6e0b393547\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222910126910/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-72c12af3-bce9-46eb-97d0-95902004bb38\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3ebd8034-00a0-49ab-b741-91b90e17e83a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-39e78450-207e-4c1b-93b8-d51f7e12b63b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>3면접착</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-6f8efcb1-65f2-4047-9d8b-48eb1a56770c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5a2b53e7-0f9a-4579-9446-f23547843214\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">3면 접착은 작업의 편의성을 위해 3면을 접착하여 딸그락 끼우는 방식의 마감 방법입니다. B형박스나 기타 마무리 공정에 많이 쓰이며 납품이나 조립시 편리함이 있습니다. 3면접착이 아닌 날개식의 조립으로 마감하는 박스도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-01fceaee-8c69-4bca-9690-2fb3ba6b11f8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-40eef1f0-dd0f-4f4f-81b7-bb51b1dc5ea8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2004b01e-1008-474a-bfcc-18e5609a3fa0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-247e1a4a-98dc-4419-b221-a02789fd6ee1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>뚜껑혀</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-9e00994a-5fb5-45db-96db-fbdf01eef099\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c5dcfc81-30b8-4ed5-ab06-822a3d397e66\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">상단의 끼우는 부분을 뚜껑혀라고 표현합니다. 보통 라운드로 처리하여 잘 끼울 수 있도록 만들고 스톱바로 잘 열리지 않도록 마무리하는 것이 보통입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-fcc9dac4-a35b-4a89-bfbd-57d5974e9d95\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9d5e711d-d518-489a-b821-5c0fc05ef454\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f4b965a-cae2-4239-973a-7703aa21e778\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8d7a5f6c-6ad5-45e6-bffc-ea3367369430\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>스톱바</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-c978d786-f3a3-4dd3-8525-7c801fdf6183\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-27d72f8e-be91-4a80-a175-fcc454fd5b63\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">뚜껑부분이 닫고나서 잘 열리지 않도록 스톱바를 만들어서 마무리합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-279f6965-12cd-4d91-9416-878065e92234\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-beaacb7e-d3d1-449d-b7a6-4704a6cd88bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-78d683a4-3e69-432a-b444-35df56259dd0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-08854ba9-047e-41a0-99e8-58918d8edc05\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>뚜껑손톱</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-c2aa4965-443c-4260-9adb-53e3838de60f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-90f29380-b952-41af-a773-37b52fc232bd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">손톱은 뚜껑을 잘 닫을 수 있도록 라운드로 모양을 내는 작업을 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-fc5fe603-e15b-4b40-b02a-fb6a125f04b9\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7c32b701-9b47-4f12-9bb1-405a948e5606\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-04140486-05a9-4fbe-8abe-90595d85b494\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-854469a4-0ee1-4768-a012-fa751e843744\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>날개</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-ed34d587-4e74-4f11-adb8-9a628b1fcdbd\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e0539e7c-fb76-44b6-895f-ea90020c5482\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">뚜껑 측면에 보조적으로 날개를 만들어서 쏟아지거나 내용물 부분을 보호하기 위해 만듭니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-938e66a0-a886-452c-a1be-e7b5b5d991f8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9559edb8-eef9-4c19-9353-55bc778e22e1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-50c72f26-30f7-4b69-bede-1fb54ca8c9cc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f49f0c76-37f4-430a-af12-638a8be47a29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222910126910/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2e0b1721-8005-40e6-83cd-cf34711b13ba\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cb82f2fe-01a6-4fcc-bc0b-8eccd092a6b6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"