d=\"SE-7c72c6a8-69c0-4439-9ea3-151e48fb3b84\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f1ee9346-160e-4bbb-a094-b27de77b1661\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c49648be-d593-47a6-ae97-58fa6a7329a3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>박스 주문시 데이터 전송 예</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5c01f9f0-e9ad-42f8-ac55-39175e6c0148\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f323d01e-06d6-4507-ab89-9db3807656b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222910126910/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a48eb76-f94f-410e-9a8e-a3d920d5e3c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4954e43-72f2-46fa-a488-02910b4cef6c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-69af8ffc-ec9c-4891-a0af-489a3bd3f33a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>주문시 주의점</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-241afd13-7f8e-4c6b-9588-682443898159\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9f76ac93-46bc-4130-a4e2-057186959163\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">1. 풀칠 부분에 인쇄나 코팅이 없도록하는것이 좋습니다. 그래야 잉크로 작업이 되어있지 않은 부분에 풀이 잘 묻어 접착력에 문제가 발생하지 않게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f4e8f5df-d55a-44f1-9e88-1dbd83060626\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f7da4379-b6e7-4141-96b8-0b0779e5af2c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">2. 하단 3면 접착부분도 합지가 아닌 원지 박스인 경우 마찬가지로 인쇄가 없도록하는 것이 좋습니다. 다만 골판지와 합지로 작업되는 경우는 인쇄가 전체적으로 작업되기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0a1d4bd6-a07f-4695-9bf6-690152556596\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d0b4adba-b9aa-4df8-a77a-3c7dfe5da80a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">3. 상단 뚜껑의 디자인 상하를 반드시 확인하시기 바랍니다. 뚜껑을 여는 곳의 위치를 고려하여 디자인하시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-05939f5e-403d-497b-9a11-a409d9e43fd7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5a5c4808-e7ad-4fb1-8e9b-99fa3024b68f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b72e8d8-21a6-47fe-941a-7559f33f511f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c5a59c6d-5e92-4697-a3bd-1d842aa4f3f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-2d7497e3-a2fc-4125-8f55-7c5620f7e505\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-975d8978-ea5b-41e5-b81b-0bafafcf5b51\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-26cec2d7-2f7c-4662-9fba-99769b00e3b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니이 찾는 리퍼럴(referral)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b930b371-fb1a-4cb0-b2b5-c059d9f9663d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3813cd1-5384-4ad2-a764-1f25a219ef5a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b294a793-ddfa-42a6-855e-faa4e082dde1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 찾는 리퍼럴은?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1c425d96-6ae0-43c3-9e07-e1e2cba09b7c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-352f382b-7deb-458e-b845-e791e3169ea9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">각 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4f927edd-b2be-4a13-a236-228590592e43\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>쇼핑몰을 운영하여 박스 디자인과 주문이 빈번한 대표님</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b12a0432-eecb-4f0b-9e02-a29759c835ec\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-acbda443-4bef-48d3-9662-fdc8d8004ed7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e90ec9d0-6313-4944-96bb-28ef40bc292a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42ed5d7a-d6b4-43a2-a187-e67b3bf55e4f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:736px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222910126910/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7abc6af9-5e36-4903-a3fd-5c5355652147\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a0e2e8ca-67c2-4a28-af39-5509f7affd82\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-75dac0d0-9833-4076-a596-55843d416057\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
